logic

Class EntitiesContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.EntitiesContainer

  • public class EntitiesContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    The EntitiesContainer class is a container for storing multiple entities and an optional customer interface. It provides methods to set and retrieve these entities and the customer interface.
